<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>HBC Radio - Rock e Heavy Metal</title>

  <style>
    *{
      margin:0;
      padding:0;
      box-sizing:border-box;
    }

    body{
      background:#111;
      color:white;
      font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }

    header{
      background:#000;
      padding:20px 60px;
      display:flex;
      justify-content:space-between;
      align-items:center;
      border-bottom:3px solid #c40000;
    }

    .logo{
      font-size:32px;
      font-weight:bold;
      color:#fff;
    }

    nav a{
      color:white;
      text-decoration:none;
      margin-left:25px;
      font-weight:bold;
    }

    nav a:hover{
      color:#c40000;
    }

    .hero{
      height:500px;
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      justify-content:center;
      align-items:center;
      text-align:center;
      background:linear-gradient(#000,#1d1d1d);
    }

    .hero h1{
      font-size:60px;
      margin-bottom:15px;
    }

    .hero p{
      font-size:22px;
      color:#cccccc;
    }

    .botao{
      margin-top:35px;
      background:#c40000;
      color:white;
      padding:15px 35px;
      border-radius:8px;
      text-decoration:none;
      font-size:20px;
      font-weight:bold;
    }

    section{
      max-width:1200px;
      margin:auto;
      padding:70px 20px;
    }

    h2{
      margin-bottom:30px;
      border-left:5px solid #c40000;
      padding-left:12px;
    }

    .cards{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
      gap:25px;
    }

    .card{
      background:#1b1b1b;
      border-radius:10px;
      overflow:hidden;
    }

    .imagem{
      height:200px;
      background:#333;
    }

    .texto{
      padding:20px;
    }

    footer{
      text-align:center;
      padding:40px;
      background:#000;
      border-top:3px solid #c40000;
      margin-top:60px;
    }
  </style>

</head>

<body>

<header>

<div class="logo">
HBC RADIO
</div>

<nav>
<a href="#">Home</a>
<a href="#">Notícias</a>
<a href="#">Programação</a>
<a href="#">Contato</a>
</nav>

</header>

<section class="hero">

<h1>ROCK E HEAVY METAL 24 HORAS</h1>

<p>
A trilha sonora perfeita para quem vive o rock.
</p>

<a class="botao" href="#">
▶ Ouvir Agora
</a>

</section>

<section>

<h2>Últimas Notícias</h2>

<div class="cards">

<div class="card">
<div class="imagem"></div>
<div class="texto">
<h3>Primeira notícia</h3>
<p>Em breve você publicará aqui suas matérias.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="imagem"></div>
<div class="texto">
<h3>Segunda notícia</h3>
<p>Especial sobre bandas e álbuns clássicos.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="imagem"></div>
<div class="texto">
<h3>Terceira notícia</h3>
<p>Programação e novidades da HBC Radio.</p>
</div>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<footer>

© 2026 HBC Radio

</footer>

</body>

</html>